WEBVTT

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:01.320
not just billions.

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:05.816
So if we're going to make
lasting and significant progress

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:08.816
in the big challenges in our world,

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:10.656
we need business,

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:13.976
both the companies and the investors,

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:15.520
to drive the solutions.

00:01:16.760 --> 00:01:20.040
So let's talk about
what business should do.

00:01:21.120 --> 00:01:22.456
And when I say that,

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:26.576
you probably think that I'm going
to talk about corporate philanthropy

00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:29.216
or corporate social responsibility.

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:32.056
CSR is the norm today,